OL,5, Richard Sharp is facing renewed        
OL,6, pressure to stand down as BBC chairman.
OL,8,FJonathan Dimbleby and Baroness         
OL,9,FWheatcroft have joined a growing chorus
OL,10,Fof voices questioning his position.    
OL,12,FMr Sharp is facing criticism for his   
OL,13,Frole in facilitating a #800,000 loan   
OL,14,Ffor then-prime minister Boris Johnson. 
OL,16,FAn MPs' committee said Mr Sharp made   
OL,17,F"significant errors of judgement" in   
OL,18,Fdoing so while applying for the BBC    
OL,19,Fjob. He insists he got the job on      
OL,20,Fmerit.                                 
